{"tid":1430583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[LASER 錫！春！袋！] 跪求文宣IT部入黎！！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:03:11.000Z","uid":117886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a59549eeea58a282cec63b88cb8ec89253d1b3","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:00:50.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩諗左個方法可以比更多人知道最update既遊行集會資料，想請咁多位文宣巴絲入黎捉laser長談一下，睇下可唔可行。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">問題</span></strong><br />\n唔好話中間派，老豆老母，有時連我地自己友都未必追得切post去睇究竟下一次遊行，集會係會係咩地方幾點開始完結。搞到次次都會集會前都好似deadline fighter咁，自己壓力大左之餘，效果又冇咁好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解決方法</span></strong><br />\n以我好似今日出煙果張報紙咁薄既Google知識，我記得Google Calendar係可以<span style=\"color: orange;\">set一個public既Calendar出黎比人follow</span>。我地會唔會可以同呢個Function黎同大家announce黎緊個時間表係點樣，每個活動既詳細情況?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個calendar event可以<span style=\"color: orange;\">落唔同tag，例如唔同顏色代表遊行定集會，有不反書定冇不反書，重勇武定重和理非等等。</span>同時，calendar event入面個<span style=\"color: orange;\">details位置可以比我地放番相關果個event既文宣圖</span>，令到成件事更加有系統。幫到啲冇追post追得好貼既巴絲佢地用到最update既文宣圖同埋資料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣亦都可以比更多人放活動入自己既Calendar，將抗爭變成生活一部分。<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點？第一次打策略野，有錯既話大家唔好用咁高ｗ數黎鍚我春袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c568f064536fc98088d74da378da04c34e622968","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"訓前自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32478432c5b288fb449e2b500f31c7a8cda3526f","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:02:02.000Z","msg":"大家睇完覺得岩又幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caae330dfb7d9c73d1df7e04e079c84a5c41db6","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:02:39.000Z","msg":"細佬我春袋已備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d498fde8d449aa906216773d17fdb53901d494","tid":1430583,"uid":263878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:03:04.000Z","msg":"oush"},{"pid":"115b3810cb5adf6aac55cd47e4b62a6366a65808","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:03:07.000Z","msg":"只係五行欠laser <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5239908aea4b264f53998f8fcf015052b95de23c","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"黎個10連就去訓，聽日仲要番早 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf94d3d7736141fb31d46f6715d404ae6a8c0be","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:03:58.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"5cc4caba3558af179b186be30790ebcfac7ab9c4","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:04:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"68e9f461abc3d2f2e7ee0ef2facf38ec8d901fad","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:04:21.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3359260ce09f3edd568c888dc54cf84909174248","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:04:34.000Z","msg":"柒"},{"pid":"7349531da22c1e924200f00995f1e7cea7c5b82d","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:05:07.000Z","msg":"陸"},{"pid":"acc9c152584b0580a2717f85cdd091da7ec192dc","tid":1430583,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:05:21.000Z","msg":"Five"},{"pid":"dcab5eb146f6ef51e26ae5820b9de1b3b97d6e17","tid":1430583,"uid":11